messages.content: Tomato Bar is great. How about 130pm at Tomato Bar?
Sorry for late at night. Tatiana wants to have lunch at Tomato Bar. Is it possible?? And yeah we should try to find another day when Rina can come too:)

If Tatiana and you do want to get lunch, let's do that. We could go to Round the Clock restaurant (or some other place) tomorrow - maybe around 1pm. But if that won't work, no problem. Either way, we should try to do something another weekend, when Rina can come.
Good morning! I can do that but Rina is not available tomorrow. I will ask Tatiana if she wants to come, or should we find another day?

Hikaru, sorry for the late notice, but would you be able to do something tomorrow, on Sunday, instead of today? My friend Ricky is busy today. If you and Rina want to have lunch with us tomorrow, let me know. Tatiana could come too if she wants.

Hi! I sent the same message on Messages but I often have troubles with receiving messages. Maybe because of my Japanese number sorry. I asked Rina ( the other Japanese) if she is available on this Saturday. But she can't make it because she will be in Chicago from Friday night to Sunday. She also wants to have lunch together, so is there another available days for you?? Because it's thanksgiving break, we both are not on Campus from 19th to 27th. Sorry. I hope we can figure out what date would work.
